tournament.name: KQ 45
tournament.registration_message:
[TONE: FUTURE] RECEIVING TRANSMISSION

Greetings denizens of this humble galaxy! Our capital Snailship will be arriving at Logan Arcade on Friday June 27th 2025.
Get ready to tap and boogie with DJ Jivan Ivan & his holocrate of cosmic disco 45s. Prepare your best away team for tough competition on Saturday & Sunday.  Then chase that last glow of twilight Sunday night before we warp back to our homelands with berries of plenty. 

** TO SECURE A T-SHIRT YOU MUST PROVIDE YOUR SIZE BY JUNE 12TH. This is a hard deadline.

* Please make sure to read our code of conduct (linked below), you will be held to it at both Logan Arcade and Kitchen 17 at all times. Please treat both venues with respect and be harmonious guests! 

* 💸  We are asking anyone who is able, to contribute ANY AMOUNT to a ticket payment support pool. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form ❤️

* 🫂 if you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due

### Thanks! We look forward to seeing you all. If you have any questions reach out to us at kqchicago@gmail.com or the discord.

Greetings denizens of this humble galaxy! Our capital Snailship will be arriving at Logan Arcade on Friday June 27th 2025.
Get ready to tap and boogie with DJ Jivan Ivan & his holocrate of cosmic disco 45s. Prepare your best away team for tough competition on Saturday & Sunday.  Then chase that last glow of twilight Sunday night before we warp back to our homelands with berries of plenty. 

** TO SECURE A T-SHIRT YOU MUST PROVIDE YOUR SIZE BY JUNE 12TH. This is a hard deadline.

* Please make sure to read our code of conduct (linked below), you will be held to it at both Logan Arcade and Kitchen 17 at all times. Please treat both venues with respect and be harmonious guests! 

* 💸  We are asking anyone who is able, to contribute ANY AMOUNT to a ticket payment support pool. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form ❤️

* 🫂 if you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due

### Thanks! We look forward to seeing you all. If you have any questions reach out to us at kqchicago@gmail.com or the discord.

Greetings denizens of this humble galaxy! Our capital Snailship will be arriving at Logan Arcade on Friday June 27th 2025.
Get ready to tap and boogie with DJ Jivan Ivan & his holocrate of cosmic disco 45s. Prepare your best away team for tough competition on Saturday & Sunday.  Then chase that last glow of twilight Sunday night before we warp back to our homelands with berries of plenty. 

** TO SECURE A T-SHIRT YOU MUST PROVIDE YOUR SIZE BY JUNE 12TH. This is a hard deadline.

* Please make sure to read our code of conduct (linked below), you will be held to it at both Logan Arcade and Kitchen 17 at all times. Please treat both venues with respect and be harmonious guests! 

* 💸  We are asking anyone who is able, to contribute ANY AMOUNT to a ticket payment support pool. It will be spread equitably across all players who need assistance. Just enter an amount in addition to your ticket at the bottom of this form ❤️

* 🫂 if you need help with your ticket, just fill out the form and click save info instead of going through payment. We will follow up with you later if any money is due

### Thanks! We look forward to seeing you all. If you have any questions reach out to us at kqchicago@gmail.com or the discord.
tournament.payment_message: Credits Accepted. Your patronage is appreciated.
